headline: UBS Points to Pricing Strength Behind Nucor’s (NUE) Share Gains
summary: Nucor Corporation (NYSE:NUE) is included among the Dividend Growth Stocks: 25 Aristocrats. On January 28, UBS analyst Andrew Jones cut Nucor Corporation (NYSE:NUE) to Neutral from Buy and raised the firm’s price target to $183 from $168.
